o", "images of texts, facebook pages, etc used as supporting evidence. Or edited versions of these documents which", "do not contain the entire conversation to keep within page limits. In high conflict cases that involve repeated", "verbal abuse, stalking behaviors, and harassment, electronic messages can support and proof other\u2019s poor", "behavior. Rather than page limit documentary evidence (i.e. police reports), a rule explaining best use of", "material would be better service. i.e. Photographs, text messages, email, electronic communications,", "depositions and similar material should only be used as exhibits if referenced and text included from these", "documents in the body of the parties declaration. All exhibits should be clearly printed and legible for ease of", "reading. Exhibits should not exceed 15 pages."], "bbox": [[0.058824, 0.058124, 0.6023780000000001, 0.027758], [0.058824, 0.087731, 0.09277699999999998, 0.022553], [0.156634, 0.138066, -0.0040939999999999865, 0.019125], [0.174739, 0.156362, -0.004082000000000002, 0.019125], [0.058824, 0.174727, 0.07829400000000002, 0.019125], [0.117647, 0.192953, 0.7995490000000001, 0.019083], [0.117647, 0.211248, 0.7885519999999999, 0.019083], [0.117647, 0.229544, 0.820759, 0.019083], [0.117647, 0.247839, 0.764427, 0.019083], [0.117647, 0.266135, 0.7874460000000001, 0.019083], [0.117647, 0.28443, 0.06145200000000001, 0.019083], [0.156634, 0.312839, -0.0040939999999999865, 0.019125], [0.174731, 0.331134, -0.004073999999999994, 0.019125], [0.058824, 0.349499, 0.07829400000000002, 0.019125], [0.117647, 0.367725, 0.412372, 0.019083], [0.156634, 0.396122, -0.0040939999999999865, 0.019125], [0.174731, 0.414417, -0.004073999999999994, 0.019125], [0.058824, 0.432782, 0.07829400000000002, 0.019125], [0.117647, 0.451008, 0.8053509999999999, 0.019083], [0.117647, 0.469304, 0.7184029999999999, 0.019083], [0.117647, 0.4977, 0.7776750000000001, 0.019083], [0.117647, 0.515996, 0.770683, 0.019083], [0.117647, 0.534291, 0.31057